      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a definitive example of high-revving Bavarian precision. Under the hood, the S54 3.2L inline-six features individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system that pulls flawlessly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, tactile engagement, paired with a factory limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. The chassis is in exemplary condition, with verified subframe integrity and a suspension setup that retains its original damping profile. This vehicle is mechanically indistinguishable from its showroom debut, free of common wear patterns and optimized for the discerning enthusiast who demands peak performance and structural purity.",
