    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional, showroom-quality 2021 BMW M340i in Mineral White Metallic. This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, having been meticulously kept in a climate-controlled garage since its initial purchase. The exterior is flawless, featuring a professional-grade ceramic coating that protects the deep, lustrous paint; there are zero stone chips, scratches, or swirl marks to be found. The interior is equally pristine, with the Cognac Vernasca leather remaining supple and completely free of wear, creases, or odors. Every tech feature, from the Head-Up Display to the Harman Kardon surround sound system, functions perfectly. Mechanically, this car is peerless, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by BMW master technicians. It has never seen inclement weather and has been driven with the utmost care. This is a rare find for a discerning buyer seeking a vehicle that looks and performs exactly as it did the day it left the factory. Includes both original keys, all manuals, and a custom-fitted indoor car cover.",
